# Sports Day — Supabase configuration
# Shared "Caerus" project (dlcseuejvducbsjhqvze). This app namespaces every table with the
# `sportsday_` prefix so it coexists with the other apps in the project.
#
# The ANON key is a PUBLIC key — it is meant to ship in a static front-end. Row Level Security
# (RLS) on the sportsday_ tables is what actually protects the data. Never put a service-role key here.

SUPABASE_URL=https://dlcseuejvducbsjhqvze.supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here
